### Storage integration
#### [NEW] `src/core/storage/programStateStore.ts` (or reuse existing Zustand store)
A unified store or context that persists strictly to LocalStorage / AsyncStorage / Supabase. Ensures completion actions process exactly once (idempotent checks). 

